title: Lisa Wingate-Never Say Never
description: From best-selling author Lisa Wingate comes Never Say Never, an enthralling blend of small-town charm and wholesome romance. Kai Miller has never put down roots and doesn't intend to change. Yet when a hurricane evacuation brings her to Daily, Texas, she begins to reexamine her tumbleweed ways. After meeting Kemp Eldridge, she can almost see herself settling down-until her dreams are dashed when she hears he's promised to another. But locals have learned to never say never-especially when Aunt Donnetta is cooking up a scheme
